local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["strait"]={"strait","[streɪt]","[stret]","n.海峡",'n.海峡,困境|||adj.困难的,窘迫的|||adj.','A province of southeast China on the East China Sea and the Formosa ||Strait||. Agriculture and fishing are important to its economy. Fuzhou is the capital. Population, 27,130,000.','福建中国东南部的一个省份，濒临东海和台湾海峡。经济以农业和渔业为主，省会为福州。人口27，130，000','Danish navigator and explorer who in1728 sailed through the Bering ||Strait||, proving(though he did not realize it at the time) that Asia and North America are separate continents.','白令，维图斯1681－1741丹麦航海家、探险家，1728年驾船穿越白令海峡，证明（尽管他当时不知道）亚洲和北美洲是两片分开的大陆'}
